pandoc

  output-file: index.html

  title-prefix: R. Heller
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long

    template: jolla
    links:
      - icon: twitter
        text: Twitter
        href: 'https://twitter.com'
      - icon: linkedin
        text: LinkedIn
        href: 'https://linkedin.com'
      - icon: github
        text: Github
        href: 'https://github.com'
